# NOTE: We intentionally do NOT ignore:
#   - external/
#   - *.lib
#   - *.dll
#
# If you later add any broad ignore like `*.lib`, make sure to
# re-include your vendor libs with rules like:
#   !external/glfw/**
#   !external/glad/**
#   !external/glm/**
